Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.39,0:00:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No matter what I do, I can't stop loving Ryuuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.97,0:00:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I want him to be with Minorin,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.18,0:00:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but it's just too painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.91,0:00:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It hurts. It really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.50,0:00:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.94,0:00:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}U-Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.47,0:00:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I was half asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.23,0:00:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This all must be very traumatic for you, considering you're such good friends with Aisaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Since you just had a nightmare, Takasu-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}let me remind you that the printout is due tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll repeat it again for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.90,0:00:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.91,0:01:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's stop here for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.43,0:02:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In the end, we weren't seriously injured, and the rescue team saved us;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:03:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then Taiga's real mother came to pick her up at the resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.71,0:03:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you contact her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.26,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The teacher told me that Aisaka isn't doing so great,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.15,0:03:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so she's resting at her parents' place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.13,0:03:15.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you hear anything about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I couldn't reach her cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have a favor to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.03,0:03:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Pretend that you're the one who saved Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If Taiga asks about it, tell her she was unconscious the whole time and said nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.59,0:03:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this related to the favor Taiga asked me on New Year's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.01,0:03:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taka-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Want to go out somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.52,0:04:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Somewhere nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.42,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, let's eat some good food!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't let Taiga be the only thing on your{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.59,0:04:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aren't the people inside taking a bit too long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Takasu, I'm not keeping you from cooking dinner, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry for forcing you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay, I won't go home until I taste the food here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to go home either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My parents will just ask what I'm going to do with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's no need to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This career assessment is just so they can decide how to split up the classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.60,0:04:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Notocchi, you're going into liberal arts, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I want to go into liberal arts and become an editor for a music magazine,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}then finally become a freeloader.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.65,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd be happy just to graduate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, I'll have to work for my dad anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry for being surprised, but you guys are actually thinking about your futures...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taka-chan, you're smart enough that you won't have any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're going into sciences, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It should be easy for you and Master Kitamura to pass the national testing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.55,0:05:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Not really, I still haven't decided if I'm going to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.95,0:05:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, we made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come on, find a seat and sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.57,0:05:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So how's it going? Have you checked on her yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kushieda, of course{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Liberal arts!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.05,0:05:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}K-Kushieda, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm working.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What about club activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They're already over because daytime is shorter in winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So, give me your orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By the way, I'll poke your eyes out if you say coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.02,0:05:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Coal noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, three ramen please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Okay, good choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Three ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Another new job, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, the hourly wage is pretty nice, so I'll try two hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why do you have so many jo{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.58,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's going to open his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Open his eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.72,0:06:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.38,0:06:33.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Endless Circle of Transmigration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks, please come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She never changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Next please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We would never have guessed she rejected you if you hadn't told us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Girls are such unpredictable creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Speaking of which, how are things going with Maya-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's still ignoring me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.31,0:07:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A girl's feelings, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is she not back because she's really not feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.12,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}or is her mother being selfish like her father and not letting her come?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}I can't stop...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.74,0:07:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...did she realize I heard her say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.39,0:07:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}...loving Ryuuji.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:52.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Career assessment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just put something like "I'll study hard" and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.97,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I make it to a four year college, how much money do you think it'll cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, don't worry about money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.74,0:08:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here, fermented soybean bomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.37,0:08:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're different from me because you're smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}After receiving a fabulous education,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}your fabulous talents will launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll be able to live a fabulous life!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, isn't there a saying {\fscx300}-{\fscx100} what was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um, gold jewel... something polish...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Golden stone... shining or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.11,0:08:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"A jewel won't shine if it isn't polished"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan, you're like shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I work and make around fifty thousand a month...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no working!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Working at Inage-san's is just an exception within an exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How do you know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to study if you work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also, we won't be able to have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.70,0:09:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A life like that is pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be happy at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But you always tell me to go to college{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.07,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right! There's always a way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She's always been like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, you're no different from other children even if you don't have a father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.23,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm an amazing mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll be perfectly happy forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Perfectly happy forever, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't worry about Taiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga said before that she's on good terms with her real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think she's probably happy to be around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.24,0:10:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That'd be great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Kushieda.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, Takasu, you're here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.79,0:10:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you're here for the budget estimate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, I'll turn it in later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.08,0:10:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, I'll be counting on you, new team captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.58,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.56,0:10:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My, the new Student Council President is sure busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}New team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.57,0:10:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Weren't you already the team captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, Kitamura's student council is really busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.02,0:10:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}so they merged the male and the female softball team,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.07,0:10:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and I was appointed the new team captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.78,0:11:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll probably become as busy as Kitamura-kun because I'm unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Then why are you getting another job?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Won't that make you busier?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.59,0:11:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Haven't you heard the saying that young people must endure hardship, Takasu-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.30,0:11:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wouldn't that hinder both sides{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.35,0:11:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm working hard because I don't want to hinder anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's because it's something that can be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something that can be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, it's Amin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're beautiful as usual today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's with that attitude, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Stupidity is contagious, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.90,0:11:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}When the child is not here, the father can do anything he wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where are you going, Kawashima?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Later, Takasu-kun! I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, class is about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you plan to skip first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.23,0:12:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why must it be you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.09,0:12:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I wanted to tell you this a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.17,0:12:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is there left to say after all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Actually, there's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}ghost in that gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It appears between those two vending machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard it was a heartbroken girl who took her{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.58,0:12:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't you tell me earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But nothing has happened so far, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.89,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think ghosts have their own personality too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They'll only appear in front of people who they want to see and understand them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I think I've seen a ghost before, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.81,0:13:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to yearn and get caught by something I can't see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.36,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and lose the things I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You talk too much, I don't want to hear the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You'll understand after you've heard the whole thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.06,0:13:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You want to say that if I just watch and don't interfere, everything will turn out fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever, talking to you feels like having a period.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't hesitate anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will look forward and try to get what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gosh, shut up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't hesitate anymore, I swear! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.49,0:13:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I definitely won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.01,0:13:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.71,0:13:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well, this is about your career assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry, I still haven't talked to my family about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.78,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then do you still feel the same as at the beginning of this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.66,0:14:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're an overachieving student and I expect a lot from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.57,0:14:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}that's why I'm concerned over this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's how being a teacher is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.52,0:14:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please don't have expectations in me, my family is poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.03,0:14:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So the problem is financial?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.65,0:14:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you need it, there are different scholarships and financial aids{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it strange to not go to college?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's just that I couldn't tell with just this career assessment...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.84,0:14:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How you feel about it, not how others feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.50,0:14:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.39,0:14:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? Why is it so dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wha{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.15,0:15:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So that's what she means by "It's all right! There's always a way!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't she also say it'd be pointless if a mother and son didn't have dinner together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ryuu-chan, you're like shining when you study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.44,0:15:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.18,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can I give it to her now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}How is a love letter embarrassing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Disgusting, isn't it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.83,0:15:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}Since I don't have the guts to confess to her, I just have to imagine like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\i1}It's horribly miserable, but I don't think of it as embarrassing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's right, the feeling of liking someone is not embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't say that to the person who likes me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.69,0:16:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just can't say it even if I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.67,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Moreover, she's not answering my calls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.27,0:16:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yasuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously, why are you work{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-T-T-T{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where were you and who were you with?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You nearly killed me. You idiot, pig, dog, yaksha, asura, gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No running!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.41,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You tried to strangle me and look at me with weird eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I was just surprised because you appeared out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Y-You didn't even call me. I was really worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, the battery died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.49,0:17:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You have to explain everything to me in detail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you didn't come back because you{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Why did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.83,0:17:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.94,0:17:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The wound isn't that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.76,0:17:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The thing about me not doing so great was a lie. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.31,0:17:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I just wanted to skip school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.54,0:17:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I see, so you're all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I hadn't seen my mom for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We stayed at a hotel,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.83,0:17:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and we went shopping, and to restaurants and movies and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just being a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.48,0:17:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Anyway, let me in first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Didn't you say you weren't going to come over anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lost my keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm going to go in through the window from your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll use the three-second rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.71,0:17:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}C-Can you do it within three seconds?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.65,0:18:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sorry for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.23,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, why don't you have dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.32,0:18:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There are some fermented beans left, so I'll just add some onions{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.98,0:18:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay, I already had dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}O-Oh yeah, Inko-chan wants to say hi to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't he sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, it's his new greeting! He learned it recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.68,0:18:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did that ugly bird get fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.02,0:18:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}E-Exactly! It's because you're not here to stress him{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Scratch that! He's eating too much because he's so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.46,0:18:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's as ugly as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}As I thought, being with Taiga is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.33,0:18:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuuj{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.56,0:18:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How disgusting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I wasn't crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just yawning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:19:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see. It's late, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bye, ugly one. I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.29,0:19:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No... This is actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was just cleaning out stuff because I had time...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.07,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Look, I didn't have time at the end of last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.09,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm really clumsy, but I finally understood after what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.18,0:19:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even if I'm clumsy, I can still be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't stop thinking about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, did you find out Minorin's true feelings yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.23,0:19:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't tell me you didn't ask her because of the fuss I caused...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why is she worrying about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:49.50,Alternative,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I promise I won't be clumsy anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.03,0:19:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.58,0:19:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Things will definitely turn out fine between you and Minorin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, Ryuuji! Don't just stand there, come and help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.47,0:20:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I always forget to lock the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A highly secured mansion isn't always convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey, be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.02,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh yeah, I nearly forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.15,0:20:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You, Kitamura-kun and Minorin went to look for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't remember, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.33,0:20:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I mean, you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, but I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:20:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In my dreams, Kitamura-kun was carrying me on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and I muttered something stupid to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a dream, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.97,0:21:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Something stupid, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Does she want to pretend she didn't say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kitamura-kun did carry you on his back,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.22,0:21:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but you didn't say anything because you were unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.22,0:21:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's what I heard, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.96,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.45,0:21:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank God!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}For a second, I was worried that it had been real.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right, later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.44,0:21:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Good night...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Taiga?
